  "2162560": {
    "name": "超时空地牢",
    "steam_appid": 2162560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Enter the Chronosphere》</strong> 是一款结合了回合制战术和实时动作的roguelike射击游戏。跟随 <strong>Starseer</strong> 号的船员们，迎战银河威胁：吞噬现实的巨大球体。在程序生成的时间球中心展开战斗，解锁新角色、外星武器和强力协同技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/050f2165e3b06e9640f7d2965fabebe6.poster.avif?t=1771856893\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/050f2165e3b06e9640f7d2965fabebe6.webm?t=1771856893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/050f2165e3b06e9640f7d2965fabebe6.mp4?t=1771856893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时间在你这一边</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款让你有时间规划下一步行动的弹幕射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个回合之间，子弹悬浮在空中，敌人被冻结。当你移动时，一切也随之移动。在大胆行动与谨慎计划之间切换。穿越弹幕、重新装填霰弹枪、将敌人击入深坑、呼叫炮击支援，或者在被击中前及时治疗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/03383b8701725bdb27b38cac390af900.poster.avif?t=1771856893\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/03383b8701725bdb27b38cac390af900.webm?t=1771856893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/03383b8701725bdb27b38cac390af900.mp4?t=1771856893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >异域装备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将来自不同世界的武器、装备和小工具混合，打造强力组合。用横扫的激光远程焚烧敌人，使用反弹子弹从拐角射击霰弹枪，改造电锯植入外星卵，然后将孵化出的手下引爆，宛如活体炸弹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/053072a56fecea1b6d732fc294dc79d3.poster.avif?t=1771856893\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/053072a56fecea1b6d732fc294dc79d3.webm?t=1771856893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/053072a56fecea1b6d732fc294dc79d3.mp4?t=1771856893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >它们吞噬，你击败</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个时间球都包含被吞噬世界的生物群落，各有独特敌人、目标和装备。选择一个时间球挑战。从虫害肆虐的地狱球获取坐标，在西部荒野解锁闪亮的新六连发手枪，或挑战最小的球体（虽然你本该在工作）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在时间球内部，物理法则会融化：预料扭曲、突变与可掠夺的悖论。你会稳定伤口，还是现实？越往深处走，越离奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/72dcd27907d26f96429d3b2dafabcbbc.poster.avif?t=1771856893\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/72dcd27907d26f96429d3b2dafabcbbc.webm?t=1771856893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162560/extras/72dcd27907d26f96429d3b2dafabcbbc.mp4?t=1771856893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在 Starseer 号上</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在他们星舰的“舒适”环境中，我们的英雄追击银河最大的威胁：神秘的时间球。解锁具有外星技能和背景故事的新角色。完成任务学习新能力，或通过新威胁和挑战扩展游戏。征服特殊时间球获取丰厚奖励。听船员们争论轮到谁洗碗。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 德语, 简体中文, 日语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 土耳其语",
